    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Step into a preserved chapter of automotive history. This isn't merely a car; it is a time capsule draped in a finish that glows with the depth of a polished mirror. Every curve of its silhouette tells a story of elegance and aerodynamic grace, standing as a silent testament to an era when craftsmanship was a religion. Inside, the air is heavy with the rich, intoxicating aroma of hand-fitted leather and polished wood\u2014surfaces so pristine they feel untouched by time. When the engine stirs, it doesn't just run; it breathes with a smooth, rhythmic heartbeat that promises to turn every mundane errand into a grand tour. This is a rare opportunity to possess a masterpiece that looks, feels, and drives as if it just rolled off the showroom floor in a dream.",
      "price": 48750.0,
